Pytest Decorators:
@pytest.mark.skip                # Skip a Test
@pytest.mark.skipif(fn)          # skip with a condition
@pytest.mark.xfail               # Expect a Test to Fail
@pytest.mark.parametrize("", []) # Parameterize a function, argnames in first arg, values in second
@pytest.mark.filterwarnings("")  # Format is "{action}:{match}")

@pytest.fixture                  # Mark a fuction as a fixture
@pytest.mark.usefixtures(""...)  # add fixtures without listing in test args
